Steps to fetch github code to local repo

git --version

if git is not installed,
 yum install git -y
git config --global user.name "Gaurav98700"
#git config --global user.email you@example.com

git clone https://github.com/Gaurav98700/hello-world.git
git pull https://github.com/Gaurav98700/hello-world.git
ls
cd webapp/(file to be edited)
cat filename
vi filename
git status

git add .
git commit -m "modified xyz file"
(commit will effect your local repo)

To push code to GITHUB repo 
git push origin master


